main: ^This stupid car! I swear it breaks down at least once a week.
^Oh hi there! I hear you're running for mayor. I have a question for you. I am a big car guy. Are you familiar with the gear shift?
^I sure am. Park, reverse, neutral, drive, and low
^I have no idea what that is

c-0: ^The what? NO! It's Park, Reverse, Neutral, Drive, and LOW! What has this town come to. You are not getting my vote.
c-1: ^That sure is correct! If you know that, I feel like my life will be in good hands!
c-2: ^Well clearly you should work on that. We need a mayor who knows their cars!
